INSERT INTO Bet(
                relative_id,
                amount,
                profit,
                bet_info,
                game_id,
                user_id,
                coin_id,
                userseed_id,
                serverseed_id
            ) VALUES (
                (SELECT MAX(relative_id)+1 FROM Bet WHERE Bet.userseed_id = $1 AND Bet.serverseed_id=$2),
                $3,
                $4,
                $5,
                $6,
                $7,
                $8,
                $9,
                $10
            )
